    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L V8, a high-revving masterpiece with individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides lightning-fast shifts, while the M Variable Differential Lock ensures optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. This example retains its structural integrity with the factory carbon fiber roof reducing the center of gravity. Suspension geometry is tight, featuring EDC (Electronic Damper Control) for variable damping rates. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, addressing common S65 failure points. The chassis remains composed under lateral load, and the hydraulic steering rack offers the tactile feedback modern EPS units lack. A driver-focused specimen ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
